column4: Uh my firefox is dead...Or is it just me... Whenever i goto my site, http://calebgamb.on.toribash.com , it has a server error, but on my ipod touch, it works fine...Can you guys check it out and make sure its only me?
Are you just spamming your site, or is there an actual problem?
Welp, I can't replicate it here.  And by "here" we're talking from three continents.
